title: Rocket Raccoon
description:
The early adventures of the anthropomorphic Guardian of the Keystone Quadrant who features prominently in the recent Annihilation Conquest cross-over event and the current series of Guardians of the Galaxy.

This limited series was penciled by Mike Mignola and inked by Al Gordon. Issue #3 was inked by Al Milgrom.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
